high_descs: Turn around and go to the bed.
Take the knife from the bed.
Turn around and go near the potato.
Cut the potato into pieces using the knife.
Turn around and go near the sink.
Put the knife on the sink tray.
Turn around and go near the sink.
Take the potato from the sink.
Turn around and go near the microwave.
Put the potato into the microwave oven.
Then take it out and go near the sink.
Put the potato on the sink tray.
anns.task_desc: Cut the potato into pieces using the knife.

high_descs: Go straight across at the door to the bed room on the left before the end of the hall.
Pick up the knife on the bed.
Turn right at the door and go straight across to the potato in the kitchen.
Slice the potato in the sink.
Go around to the front of the sink.
Place the knife on the left side of the sink.
Go around to the back of the sink.
Pick up a slice of the potato.
Go across to the fridge and across to the microwave.
Place the potato in the microwave, heat it, take it back out the microwave.
Turn left to the sink.
Place the potato on the sink beside the knife.
anns.task_desc: Place a heated slice of Potato on the counter beside the Sink.

high_descs: Go ahead and then left to exit this room, heading straight down the hallway and taking the last door on the left, approaching the bed.
Pick up the knife from the bed.
Turn around and exit this room, turning right down the hallway until reaching the kitchen on the left, turning towards the potato.
Slice the potato in the sink.
Walk to the panel next to the sink.
Place the knife down next to the sink.
Turn back to the sliced potatoes in the sink.
Pick up one potato from the sink.
Go towards the microwave in the corner of the kitchen.
Use the microwave on the potato slice and pick the potato back up.
Turn back towards the sink.
Place the potato slice down on the panel to the left of the sink.
anns.task_desc: Place a microwaved Potato slice next to a Sink.
